import Mathlib
open Complex Set
open scoped Topology

/-- Let U ‚äÜ ‚ÑÇ be an open set and f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ a function. If f is holomorphic on U (i.e. complex-differentiable on U), then f is analytic: for every z0 ‚àà U, f is analytic at z0. Formalize as: if Open U and DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U, then ‚àÄ z0 ‚àà U, AnalyticAt ‚ÑÇ f z0. End the Lean statement with := by sorry. -/
theorem analyticAt_of_differentiableOn_ext {U : Set ‚ÑÇ} : IsOpen U ‚Üí ‚àÄ {f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ}, DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U ‚Üí ‚àÄ {z‚ÇÄ : ‚ÑÇ}, z‚ÇÄ ‚àà U ‚Üí AnalyticAt ‚ÑÇ f z‚ÇÄ := by sorry
